data.description: This is a great and amazing opportunity to get your dream home. Excellent location. House Features: 4 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, 2 car garage, stainless steel appliances. The home is set up nicely for entertaining. The interior is warm and inviting. Life's conveniences are minutes away including shopping center, restaurants, theme Parks. All information recorded in the MLS is intended to be accurate but can not guaranteed, buyer advised to verify. If exact square footage or room sizes are a concern, property should be independently measured. Seller is really motivated to sell
